From: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 03:57:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?M432:=20Switch=20fp16=E2=86=92bf16=20mode,=20fo?=
 =?UTF-8?q?rce=20ZeRO-1=20with=20cpu=5Foffload?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

FP16_UnfusedOptimizer clones fp32 master weights on GPU:
  bf16 params 25.7GB + fp32 clone 51.4GB = 77GB > A6000 47.5GB

Two fixes:
  1. fp16.enabled→bf16.enabled: BF16Optimizer keeps params in bf16
     without fp32 master copy on GPU (BF16 has 8 exponent bits =
     same dynamic range as FP32, no loss scaling needed)
  2. cpu_offload forces zero_stage >= 1: ZeRO stage 0 ignores
     offload_optimizer config. Stage 1 partitions optimizer states
     across ranks and offloads to CPU via DeepSpeedCPUAdam.

Memory after fix on A6000:
  bf16 params:     25.7GB (on GPU)
  optimizer states: 0GB   (offloaded to CPU via ZeRO-1)
  gradients:       25.7GB (but ZeRO-1 partitions across 3 GPUs → 8.6GB)
  AC activations:  ~2-4GB (per-layer checkpointing)
  Total:           ~36GB  < 47.5GB

Signed-off-by: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
---
 REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py | 5 +++--
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py b/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py
index 8de7c64..b53e3dc 100644
--- a/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py
+++ b/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py
@@ -2023,9 +2023,8 @@ class Trainer:
                     "weight_decay": config.weight_decay,
                 }
             },
-            "fp16": {
+            "bf16": {
                 "enabled": True,
-                "initial_scale_power": 16,
             },
             "desloc": {
                 "enabled": True,
@@ -2044,6 +2043,8 @@ class Trainer:
         # ZeRO optimization (supports stage 0 and 1 for all methods)
         _zero_stage = getattr(config, 'zero_stage', 0)
         _cpu_offload = getattr(config, 'cpu_offload', False)
+        if _cpu_offload and _zero_stage < 1:
+            _zero_stage = 1
         zero_cfg = {"stage": _zero_stage}
         if _cpu_offload:
             zero_cfg["offload_optimizer"] = {"device": "cpu", "pin_memory": True}
